headline: Nissay Asset Management Corporation Becomes First in Japan to Implement Broadridge's Mortgage-Backed Securities Trade Assignment Portal
summary: Broadridge Financial Solutions Inc. (NYSE: BR), a global Fintech leader, today announced that Nissay Asset Management Corporation (NAM) has implemented Broadridge's Mortgage–Backed Securities Trade Assignment Portal (TAP), becoming the first asset management company in Japan to adopt the solution.
